ğŸ“Œ 5. Failover and multi-region messaging
SNS can broadcast messages between regions for DR.

â­ SNS vs SQS (VERY IMPORTANT INTERVIEW QUESTION)
FeatureSNSSQSTypePub/SubQueueDeliveryPushPullConsumersManyOne consumer per messageMessage retentionNoYes (up to 14 days)Use caseNotifications and fan-outBackground jobs, processing tasks
SNS + SQS often used together for reliable fan-out, called SNS â†’ SQS fan-out pattern.

